rows.label: tlk41400011_05_msg0001
rows.name:
Quite the state Alst is in
these days, eh?

rows.label: tlk41400011_05_msg0002
rows.name:
Yet somehow the economy seems to
go on pretty much as usual.

rows.label: tlk41400011_05_msg0003
rows.name:
There hasn't been any looting, and the
value of money hasn't really changed.

rows.label: tlk41400011_05_msg0004
rows.name:
Maybe the people of Alst are more
full of hope than I gave them credit for.

rows.label: tlk41400011_05_msg0005
rows.name:
I hope you'll keep buying and
selling and generally contributing
to the city's economy, too.
